# 2. User Randomization

`randomization.py`

```python
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np

df = pd.read_csv(
    "data/user_sessions.csv"
)

np.random.seed(42)

df["Variant"] = np.random.choice(
    ["Control","Treatment"],
    size=len(df)
)

df.to_csv(
    "data/experiment_data.csv",
    index=False
)

print("Users randomized")
```

