# 6. Multi-Touch Attribution

`attribution.py`

```python
import pandas as pd

df = pd.read_csv(
    "data/marketing_channels.csv"
)

attribution = (
    df.groupby("Channel")
      ["Revenue"]
      .sum()
      .reset_index()
)

attribution["Contribution"] = (
    attribution["Revenue"] /
    attribution["Revenue"].sum()
)

attribution.to_csv(
    "outputs/attribution_results.csv",
    index=False
)
```

