# 8. Cohort Retention Analysis

`cohort_analysis.py`

```python
import pandas as pd

df = pd.read_csv(
    "data/transactions.csv"
)

df["OrderDate"] = pd.to_datetime(
    df["OrderDate"]
)

df["CohortMonth"] = (
    df.groupby("UserID")
      ["OrderDate"]
      .transform("min")
      .dt.to_period("M")
)

df["OrderMonth"] = (
    df["OrderDate"]
      .dt.to_period("M")
)

retention = pd.crosstab(
    df["CohortMonth"],
    df["OrderMonth"]
)

retention.to_csv(
    "outputs/cohort_retention.csv"
)
```

---

# 9. SQL Cohort Retention

`cohort_retention.sql`

```sql
WITH cohort AS
(
SELECT
UserID,
MIN(OrderDate) AS FirstOrder

FROM transactions

GROUP BY UserID
)

SELECT *
FROM cohort;
```

